tool_description: De Fi Crypto Exchange API finds the most efficient paths for a token swap, allowing asset exchanges at the best rates on the market.
title: De Fi Crypto Currency Exchange

api_list.name: swap
api_list.description: Generate data for calling the router for exchange. The data ready to send the transaction.

required_parameters.name: walletAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the wallet that calls the exchange router.

required_parameters.name: blockchainId
required_parameters.description: The blockchain id you can choose from eth, bsc, polygon, avalanche, optimism, arbitrum, gnosis.

required_parameters.name: toTokenAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the requested token.

required_parameters.name: amountTrade
required_parameters.description: The amount of tokens to trade in wei.

required_parameters.name: fromTokenAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the trade in token.

required_parameters.name: slippage
required_parameters.description: Limit of price slippage you are willing to accept in percentage, may be set with decimals. 0.5 means 0.5% slippage is acceptable. Low values increase chances that transaction will fail, high values increase chances of front running. Set values in the range from 0 to 50.

optional_parameters.name: gasPrice
optional_parameters.description: The router takes in account gas expenses to determine exchange route. It is important to use the same gas price on the quote and swap methods.Gas price set in wei 12.5 GWEI set as 12500000000.

optional_parameters.name: gaslimit
optional_parameters.description: Maximum amount of gas for a swap. Should be the same for a quote and swap. Default value 11500000

api_list.name: rate
api_list.description: Find the best quote to exchange.

required_parameters.name: blockchainId
required_parameters.description: The blockchain id you can choose from eth, bsc, polygon, avalanche, optimism, arbitrum, gnosis.

required_parameters.name: toTokenAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the requested token.

required_parameters.name: amount
required_parameters.description: The amount of tokens to trade in wei.

required_parameters.name: fromTokenAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the trade in token.

api_list.name: approve
api_list.description: Generate data for calling the contract in order to allow the router to spend funds. The data ready to send the approval transaction.

required_parameters.name: blockchainId
required_parameters.description: The blockchain id you can choose from eth, bsc, polygon, avalanche, optimism, arbitrum, gnosis.

required_parameters.name: amount
required_parameters.description: The number of tokens that the router is allowed to spend in wei. If not specified, it will be allowed to spend an infinite amount of tokens.

required_parameters.name: tokenAddress
required_parameters.description: The address of the token you want to exchange.

api_list.name: tokens
api_list.description: Returns a list of tokens available for swap in the selected blockchain. All supported tokens (can also use your own).

required_parameters.name: blockchainId
required_parameters.description: The blockchain id you can choose from eth, bsc, polygon, avalanche, optimism, arbitrum, gnosis.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://de-fi-crypto-currency-exchange.p.rapidapi.com/tokens/{blockchainid}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "de-fi-crypto-currency-exchange.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
